OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWet and very
OL,6,Fwindy weather will sweep north and
OL,7,Feastwards across the UK tonight. The
OL,8,Fworst of the conditions are likely
OL,9,Facross some central and northern areas
OL,10,Fwhere severe gales are expected.
OL,11,FNorthwest Scotland will also have some
OL,12,Fsnow.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FStorm Dave will clear away to
OL,15,Fthe northeast tomorrow morning,
OL,16,Fleaving sunshine and showers across
OL,17,Fthe UK for Easter Sunday. The showers
OL,18,Flook particularly heavy and blustery
OL,19,Fin the north.
